        These books represent different stages of an engineering careerâ€”from
        mastering the craft to leading teams and shaping organizations. I
        believe in reading widely across technical domains and returning to
        foundational texts as you gain experience.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mt-4">
        <Icon
          name="mdi:check-circle"
          width={16}
          height={16}
          class="text-[#4CAF50]"
        />
        <span class="text-small opacity-70"
          >Books I've read and highly recommend</span
        >
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mt-2">
        <Icon
          name="mdi:bookmark-outline"
          width={16}
          height={16}
          class="text-[#ffe895] opacity-60"
        />
        <span class="text-small opacity-70">On my reading list</span>
